atiyoga|In the Nyingma system, the third of the three classes of inner tantras, in which meditation practices to actualize the immediate causes for an enlightening mind and Corpus of Forms of a Buddha are emphasized.


attachment|The disturbing emotion that exaggerates the good qualities of an object that one possesses and does not wish to let go of it.
attachment, sticky|See: sticky attachment
