hearer|See: shravaka
heart essence division|Another name for the quintessence teachings division of treasure texts, and for the texts contained in this division.
heart essence teachings|Teachings emphasizing the primal purity aspect of pure awareness.
heartwarming love|The subsidiary awareness (mental factor) with which one has a feeling of closeness and warmth toward anyone one meets.
heavenly musician|See: those who sustain themselves on fragrances
